    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 8. Lithobius anderssoni n. sp., holotype, Ƥ, Cyprus, 1 km E of Letimbou, loc. 126, 9. V. 1981, H. W. Waldén leg. (GNM): Figure 4, left ocelli and Tömösváry’s organ, scale bar 0.2 mm; Figure 5, anterior margin of forcipular coxosternite, scale bar 0.2 mm; Figure 6, TT 4 – 8, scale bar 1 mm; Figure 7, right female gonopod, ventral view, scale bar 0.1 mm; Figure 8, right female gonopod, dorsal view, scale bar 0.1 mm." ;
